{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-226-a-scoop-of-blancmange","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Zoezi la 226: Kipande cha blancmange","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Blancmange graf je skup tačaka ($x$,$y$) gde je $0 ≤ x ≤ 1$ i $\\displaystyle y = \\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty} \\frac{s(2^nx)}{2^n}$, gde je $s(x)$ rastojanje od $x$ do najbližeg celog broja.</p>\n<p>Površina ispod blancmange grafa jednaka je $\\frac{1}{2}$, prikazana ružičastom bojom na slici ispod.</p>\n<img alt=\"diagram of blancmange curve, with circle C shown on diagram\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/a-scoop-of-blancmange.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $C$ kružnica sa centrom ($\\frac{1}{4}$,$\\frac{1}{2}$) i poluprečnikom $\\frac{1}{4}$, prikazana tamnom bojom na slici.</p>\n<p>Koja površina ispod blancmange grafa je obuhvaćena kružnicom $C$? Dajte odgovor zaokružen na osam decimalnih mesta u formatu 0.abcdefgh.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4511000cf542c50ff62","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301869,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-226-a-scoop-of-blancmange"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function scoopOfBlancmange() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nscoopOfBlancmange();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>scoopOfBlancmange()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>0.11316017</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(scoopOfBlancmange(), 0.11316017);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-226-a-scoop-of-blancmange","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-227-the-chase","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-225-tribonacci-non-divisors","id":"5900f4511000cf542c50ff62","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-226-a-scoop-of-blancmange"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}